measurements.description:
Five stately flowers on one 33.5-cm, arched, unsupported
 inflorescence; sepals and petals soft pink-lavender, 
 fading to white basally, sepals linear, recurved basally,
 lateral sepals swept back, petals ovate, ruffled marginally,
 prominent midrib, slight magenta flair apically; lip ruffled,
 magenta, light pink picotee, two eye spots rich yellow, fading 
 
to white, throat light yellow, magenta veins; column pale pink,
 anther cap white, dark lavender apically; substance medium;
 texture crystalline, lip velvet.
